How to write script for videos like Kit Capture Video, Profile Video or Robot Reveal Video CD-Media: Photos

In this reply, I will talk about the different kinds of videos we make and how we plan and write the scripts, but also a little bit about editing and the structure of specific videos. Besides that, I definitely agree with the comment above, the media from 6328 is amazing! Really check them out if you have the time! An…
